snippet.title: Fe Gameplay Trailer - EA PLAY 2016
snippet.description:
Watch the Fe Gameplay Trailer and enjoy a beautiful world full of discovery, conflict and relationships. Created with the support of the Creative Europe programme of the European Union. To learn more about Zoink Games, visit here: http://www.zoinkgames.com/ 

Fe, created by a small studio based in Gothenburg, is the first game coming from EA Originals. Learn more: http://x.ea.com/7922 

EA Originals is about finding great new games that we know players are going to love, and working with small developers to make sure those games get discovered and into the hands of players.
